SubjectHellenic Republic - Double Taxation Convention Ratification
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to ratify, on behalf of Canada, the CONVENTION between Canada and the HELLENIC REPUBLIC for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital.
